{
  "stem": "182.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had such a wonderful time together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We are friends still today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when my father came home from the hospital, then I had nowhere to sleep, because I slept in the same bed with my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We only had a-- a little room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If I was sick, her mother took care on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And because I had her as a friend, I learn much faster English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "By the way, my mother spoke fluently English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my-- she taught my father in Europe yet how to speak English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I heard English all the time in the house, but I didn't know how to speak.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and this family, as I say, they had a tremendous influence on me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And-- and I found life in America wonderful-- Williamsburg, with the-- all the-- the-- the through and through Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And to hear on the bus, the-- the black or the Gentile bus driver say, gesundheit, and to hear on the radio or in nightclubs Jewish words, but they were-- it-- it was something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then I got a letter one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I met a man who was our former landlord.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he says, oh, it's a good thing I see you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "A letter came for you, and I didn't know where you moved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I didn't know how to give this to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he pulls out of his pocket a crumpled up old letter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he gives it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I take it home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I read it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say to my mother, a man is writing to me a letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know who he is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But why is he writing me a letter?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
